  {
    "eu_id": "EU-0005",
    "kind": "section_text_panel",
    "page": "yanbaor2_0071908e787f90267682e19ef093bb18dda6e1c1614534c445ddd62c425b3a94.pdf_44",
    "primary_id": "docling_yanbaor2_0071908e787f90267682e19ef093bb18dda6e1c1614534c445ddd62c425b3a94.pdf_44_7",
    "source": "header_anchor",
    "member_count": 5,
    "elements": [
      {
        "id": "docling_yanbaor2_0071908e787f90267682e19ef093bb18dda6e1c1614534c445ddd62c425b3a94.pdf_44_7",
        "observed_type": "section_header",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "DM: How does your solution integrate into the omni-channel approach?",
        "bbox": [
          0.35728952796470076,
          0.4578373013531423,
          0.6365503066495325,
          0.48412698416443256
        ],
        "order": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_yanbaor2_0071908e787f90267682e19ef093bb18dda6e1c1614534c445ddd62c425b3a94.pdf_44_8",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "RF: We are the platform that enables these omni-channel technologies to deliver a consistent, compliant and needsbased experience to customers. Our VA logic can be used to navigate staff through all known customer engagements in line with the latest regulatory, procedural and product rules — before handing over to the existing operating systems for execution.",
        "bbox": [
          0.357289527004459,
          0.49851190498979714,
          0.6406570844513677,
          0.6337209300383702
        ],
        "order": 9
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_yanbaor2_0071908e787f90267682e19ef093bb18dda6e1c1614534c445ddd62c425b3a94.pdf_44_3",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "With our solution, no matter what question a customer asks, the employee will be able to quickly consider the right factors, ask the right questions and then offer the right products or solutions. They don't need to confer with trained specialists because the logic used by those specialists is already embedded in the system. It also means staff can be performing in a fully compliant way with a fraction of traditional training.",
        "bbox": [
          0.0554414772528383,
          0.5537790699979672,
          0.33880903337026325,
          0.7021329366069478
        ],
        "order": 10
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_yanbaor2_0071908e787f90267682e19ef093bb18dda6e1c1614534c445ddd62c425b3a94.pdf_44_12",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Ryan Falkenberg Ryan Falkenberg is the co-founder and CEO of CLEVVA, a platform that allows non-coding teams to build a digital 'brain' that both staff and chatoots use to deliver the same consistent, compliant customer experience.",
        "bbox": [
          0.6796714557086394,
          0.5696924605087048,
          0.913757699066117,
          0.6642441857120301
        ],
        "order": 11
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_yanbaor2_0071908e787f90267682e19ef093bb18dda6e1c1614534c445ddd62c425b3a94.pdf_44_9",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "The natural starting point for our platform is often within the contact center — helping turn agents into Super Agents who can answer any call they receive. From there we very seamlessly integrate into the digital architecture and operating systems of the organization to help them deliver a true omni-channel experience that is consistent, compliant and customer focused.",
        "bbox": [
          0.35523614116772445,
          0.649709302325181,
          0.6406570828086574,
          0.7688953485885153
        ],
        "order": 12
      }
    ]
  },
